snippet.title: SimTown gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for SimTown (aka simtown), PC game produced by Maxis Software in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/sim-town/657/
Building a city and checking how it grow up in this interesting city simulation.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
SimLife - https://youtu.be/Q5LjhZzCzlY
SimCity 3000 - https://youtu.be/ylnjNX1Hm3g
